data.description: Serenity awaits you! This remarkable home, designed by Dick Achey, sits back on a stunning private 2.5-acre treed lot in Sunset Vista Estates! Walk through the front door of this 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home, into a spacious cathedral-vaulted ceiling living room with panoramic views of the S.F. Peaks! Views from every room in the house, it will take your breath away! The home is built of STEEL, and all high quality interior and exterior furnishings  amenities have been immaculately maintained. The master bedroom is on the main level, with another bedroom, and bonus room. Downstairs is a 3rd bedroom with the possibility of turning this into a mother-in-law quarters. Also, downstairs is a partially finished room, wonderful as-is, that could easily be used as a hobby room, exercise room, or even converted into a kitchen. The Sunset Vista subdivision of custom-built homes is surrounded on 3 sides by National Forest, with easements to N.F. for hiking! The amenities are too long to list, so please call to schedule your private showing, this will not last long!
